metadata.name: MentorCalls NFTs #001
metadata.description: MentorCalls is a collection of 500 unique NFTs. Every NFT is a unique 1/1 piece of art with a slightly different style to it. Your MentorCalls NFT gives you members-only benefits. A year from now you may wish you had started today Future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation. Visit www.mentorcalls.io for more details.
